{"tid":2203193,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納或有意開拍Joker2/3  Joaquin Phoenix身價上揚10倍至5000萬美金","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:03:35.000Z","uid":192075,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d472735c3325c5c2453cad28d25d4ce68069c7f1","tid":2203193,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YA0bfmE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYA0bfmE.jpg&h=b0c10f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外媒《Mirror》報導，電影公司華納有意開拍兩套《JOKER》續集，並向主演華堅馮力士 出價5000萬美元片酬，比第一集嘅450萬美元高出10倍有多！如果成真嘅話，今次將會係華堅馮力士演員生涯入面，最高片酬嘅一次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myfZpe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyfZpe4.jpg&h=efbc6d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，華堅馮力士本來認為《JOKER》係一部獨立電影，但依家佢都有興趣再飾演小丑一角。目前，電影公司同華堅馮力士仍處於商討階段，但有指劇本已經籌備當中，而華堅馮力士都好熱衷參與。<br />\n<br />\n《JOKER小丑》兩部續集預計未來4年內完成，並分別於2022年及2024年推出。導演 杜德菲力斯 同製作人 畢利谷巴 將會回歸。不過，由於華堅馮力士未確定參演，所以一切消息仍然有待落實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/187242217958732/posts/3974585735891009/?extid=46qEC10lthHQfIBv&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F187242217958732%2Fposts%2F3974585735891009%2F%3Fextid%3D46qEC10lthHQfIBv%26d%3Dn&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=bc70ff0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/187242217958732/posts/3974585735891009/?extid=46qEC10lthHQfIBv&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/joaquin-phoenix-offered-50million-joker-22672996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2F3am%2Fcelebrity-news%2Fjoaquin-phoenix-offered-50million-joker-22672996&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=7359f5df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/joaquin-phoenix-offered-50million-joker-22672996</a>"},{"